{"tid":2289343,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大港豬時代","createTime":"2020-11-17T07:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T07:58:44.000Z","uid":55524,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0203248d44dc075990b1e048679ab12d6e606d85","tid":2289343,"uid":55524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;想唔想要我住緊果層千呎豪宅呀？想要的話可以去台灣殺人失走佬返嚟。去馬喇！我將所有既教學都放曬上連登比大家參考。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳大喊他著名的遺言，同時管浩鳴動手執刑幫佢搞入台證，<br />\n<br />\n&quot;大粒墨&quot; 林奠&middot;C&middot;同佳就此被處死。<br />\n<br />\n使得許多住緊百呎龍床盤香港人為爭奪「DEAD BODY」而開始於取消引導條款既各國樹立霸權、極力爭奪，讓世界迎接「大港豬時代」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a7c6ed4ac6fe6996954bcd01cb46eeccc83614","tid":2289343,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}